Made a decision on my own

337
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,639
Just wanted to surprise you

338
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:58,799
Thanks for your hard work, Dong

339
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,600
Boss

340
00:16:03,559 --> 00:16:04,320
