An Dong

366
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:19,799
What's up?

367
00:17:19,799 --> 00:17:20,559
Check this out.

368
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:23,759
How to make banmian.

369
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,000
You brought this back too?

370
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:28,240
Let's give it a try.

371
00:17:29,519 --> 00:17:30,519
Spoon out and coat with sauce.

372
00:17:30,799 --> 00:17:31,440
Flash fry.

373
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,720
Every step matters.

374
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,960
I've made flash-fried meat noodles all my life.

375
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:37,079
First time I learned this.

376
00:17:38,839 --> 00:17:39,319
Right.

377
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:43,319
The meat slices should be golden.

378
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,079
With a hint of pink in the red.

379
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,920
That way, the meat stays tender.

380
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,160
